OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA sunny start becoming cloudy
OL,6,Fwith chance of some isolated thundery
OL,7,Fshowers developing in the afternoon
OL,8,Fand lingering into the evening.
OL,9,FTemperatures remaining High for the
OL,10,Ftime of year.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FGenerally dry with variable cloud on
OL,14,FWednesday and Thursday. Some sunny
OL,15,Fintervals on Friday and breezy along
OL,16,Fthe coast. Temperatures remain warm
OL,17,Fbut feeling cooler along the coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
